	<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Trivia">Trivia</span></h2>
	<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Units">Units</span></h3>
	<ul><li>Subaru is part of a unit called Oozora Family with her illustrator <a href="https://hololive.wiki/wiki/Shigure_Ui" title="Shigure Ui">Shigure Ui</a>, who acts as the mother and Nijisanji's Maimoto Keisuke, who acts as the uncle next door.</li>
		<li>She is also part of FAMS with <a href="https://hololive.wiki/wiki/Shirakami_Fubuki" title="Shirakami Fubuki">Shirakami Fubuki</a>, <a href="https://hololive.wiki/wiki/Nakiri_Ayame" title="Nakiri Ayame">Nakiri Ayame</a> and <a href="https://hololive.wiki/wiki/Ookami_Mio" title="Ookami Mio">Ookami Mio</a>, and by extension, OKFAMS, additionally including <a href="https://hololive.wiki/wiki/Nekomata_Okayu" title="Nekomata Okayu">Nekomata Okayu</a> and <a href="https://hololive.wiki/wiki/Inugami_Korone" title="Inugami Korone">Inugami Korone</a>.</li></ul>
	<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Other">Other</span></h3>
	<ul><li>Appeared as a guest as Subaru Duck in Hololive's collaboration with Dawn of the Breakers<sup id="cite_ref-36" class="reference"><a href="https://hololive.wiki/wiki/Oozora_Subaru?action=render#cite_note-36">[36]</a></sup>, then later as herself as a playable character.<sup id="cite_ref-37" class="reference"><a href="https://hololive.wiki/wiki/Oozora_Subaru?action=render#cite_note-37">[37]</a></sup></li>
		<li>She has a sister who has debuted as a VTuber.<sup id="cite_ref-38" class="reference"><a href="https://hololive.wiki/wiki/Oozora_Subaru?action=render#cite_note-38">[38]</a></sup></li>
		<li>Subaru is the origin of Cover Corp. CEO's nickname "<a href="https://hololive.wiki/wiki/YAGOO" title="YAGOO">YAGOO</a>". She once misread his family name 谷郷 (Tanigou) as YAGOO. The nickname has stuck ever since.</li>
		<li>Subaru loves western movies and studied English so she can join overseas forums to talk about movies. She likes movies in the Marvel Cinematic Universe, particularly The Avengers and Iron Man.
			<ul><li>Her favorite Avenger is Hawkeye.</li></ul></li>
		<li>Is one of the Hololive Production VTubers with a verified YouTube channel. Other verified members can be found <a href="https://hololive.wiki/wiki/Category:YouTube_Verified_Members" title="Category:YouTube Verified Members">here</a>.</li></ul>
